full_text:
For being involved in a field where no one, not even the &quot;experts&quot;, really knows anything definitively, a lot of people sure do get arrogant, and act like know it alls.... very stupid indeed.  This does not mean that everything you say has to come out sounding unsure, but it does mean that you think twice before you yell out dramatically &quot;demon!&quot; or before you discredit someone else in your own mind....

